data.name: label1.Text
data.value:
We are under attack, Corporal, we need your help! Earth is under threat of invasion by alien ships. Your starship is ready to take off to the battlefront. Together we will be able to deal with this threat and ensure the safety of our planet. Keep in mind that every decision you make will have consequences, so be careful and judicious in your actions.
Your main task is not to miss a single alien ship! To do this, you can use the arrows and activate the weapon with the "Spacebar".
